<br>
All of this would only make us better at fighting undead, since we don't get any DD spells vs anything live until 49th level.  I think this would be an excellent addition to our already strong position vs. undead, and I feel strongly that our old quest Breastplate should have <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> SOMETHING</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to set it apart from the Netherbian Chitin, especially given the cost of actually doing the quest.<br>
<br>
Thoughts? <p><div align="center"><font size="2">Aragir Lancot<BR>
<BR>
<font size="1">"One man plus the truth equals a majority."<BR>
