<br>
I think it would be pointless to upgrade any low lvl armors anyway. thoses armors were put in the game when everyone was a low lvl. There were seldom any lvl 50s running around when I started EQ years ago. Zones like MIstmore and unrest were jammed packed every night. You had to be put on lists just to camp the ghost room, hehe. Thoses were the days.<br>
<br>
